**LogDriftWeaver**  
**Description:**  
Analyzes long-term log patterns to identify slow drift in error types, message density, or warning frequencies.

```markdown
# LogDriftWeaver - Temporal Log Shift Analyzer

LogDriftWeaver visualizes how logs change over time, highlighting the slow evolution of anomalies and signals.

## Features
- Drift timeline generator  
- Frequency pattern comparison  
- CLI-based interface

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogDriftWeaver.git
cd LogDriftWeaver
python analyze.py
